{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":810,"text":"I'm a tourism entrepreneur\nand a peacebuilder,"},{"time":3968,"text":"but this is not how I started."},{"time":6824,"text":"When I was seven years old,\nI remember watching television"},{"time":9889,"text":"and seeing people throwing rocks,"},{"time":12466,"text":"and thinking, this must be\na fun thing to do."},{"time":15856,"text":"So I got out to the street\nand threw rocks,"},{"time":18201,"text":"not realizing I was supposed\nto throw rocks at Israeli cars."},{"time":22682,"text":"Instead, I ended up stoning\nmy neighbors' cars. (Laughter)"},{"time":26908,"text":"They were not enthusiastic\nabout my patriotism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30810,"text":"This is my picture with my brother."},{"time":32904,"text":"This is me, the little one,\nand I know what you're thinking:"},{"time":35739,"text":"\"You used to look cute,\nwhat the heck happened to you?\""},{"time":38680,"text":"But my brother, who is older than me,"},{"time":40631,"text":"was arrested when he was 18,"},{"time":43045,"text":"taken to prison on charges\nof throwing stones."},{"time":45994,"text":"He was beaten up when he refused\nto confess that he threw stones,"},{"time":49570,"text":"and as a result, had internal injuries"},{"time":52171,"text":"that caused his death soon after\nhe was released from prison."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56814,"text":"I was angry, I was bitter,"},{"time":60460,"text":"and all I wanted was revenge."}]},{"cues":[{"time":64152,"text":"But that changed when I was 18."},{"time":66659,"text":"I decided that I needed\nHebrew to get a job,"},{"time":70096,"text":"and going to study Hebrew\nin that classroom"},{"time":72603,"text":"was the first time I ever met Jews\nwho were not soldiers."},{"time":78037,"text":"And we connected over really small things,\nlike the fact that I love country music,"},{"time":82919,"text":"which is really strange\nfor Palestinians."},{"time":86646,"text":"But it was then that I realized also\nthat we have a wall of anger,"},{"time":91306,"text":"of hatred and of ignorance\nthat separates us."},{"time":96919,"text":"I decided that it doesn't matter\nwhat happens to me."},{"time":101418,"text":"What really matters is how I deal with it."},{"time":104111,"text":"And therefore, I decided\nto dedicate my life"},{"time":107455,"text":"to bringing down the walls\nthat separate people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":111843,"text":"I do so through many ways."},{"time":113863,"text":"Tourism is one of them,\nbut also media and education,"},{"time":116963,"text":"and you might be wondering,\nreally, can tourism change things?"},{"time":120657,"text":"Can it bring down walls? Yes."},{"time":122367,"text":"Tourism is the best sustainable way\nto bring down those walls"},{"time":127087,"text":"and to create a sustainable way\nof connecting with each other"},{"time":131472,"text":"and creating friendships."}]},{"cues":[{"time":134026,"text":"In 2009, I cofounded Mejdi Tours,"},{"time":137811,"text":"a social enterprise that\naims to connect people,"},{"time":141271,"text":"with two Jewish friends, by the way,"},{"time":143732,"text":"and what we'll do, the model we did,"},{"time":146031,"text":"for example, in Jerusalem,\nwe would have two tour guides,"},{"time":149537,"text":"one Israeli and one Palestinian,\nguiding the trips together,"},{"time":152996,"text":"telling history and narrative\nand archaeology and conflict"},{"time":156201,"text":"from totally different perspectives."},{"time":159173,"text":"I remember running a trip together\nwith a friend named Kobi --"},{"time":162531,"text":"Jewish congregation from Chicago,\nthe trip was in Jerusalem --"},{"time":165555,"text":"and we took them to a refugee camp,\na Palestinian refugee camp,"},{"time":168717,"text":"and there we had this amazing food."},{"time":170817,"text":"By the way, this is my mother. She's cool."},{"time":173700,"text":"And that's the Palestinian\nfood called maqluba."},{"time":176254,"text":"It means \"upside-down.\""},{"time":177571,"text":"You cook it with rice and chicken,\nand you flip it upside-down."},{"time":180795,"text":"It's the best meal ever."},{"time":182436,"text":"And we'll eat together."},{"time":183744,"text":"Then we had a joint band,\nIsraeli and Palestinian musicians,"},{"time":186548,"text":"and we did some belly-dancing."},{"time":188405,"text":"If you don't know any,\nI'll teach you later."},{"time":191795,"text":"But when we left, both sides,"},{"time":194907,"text":"they were crying because\nthey did not want to leave."},{"time":197484,"text":"Three years later, those\nrelationships still exist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201106,"text":"Imagine with me\nif the one billion people"},{"time":203916,"text":"who travel internationally \nevery year travel like this,"},{"time":207724,"text":"not being taken in the bus\nfrom one side to another,"},{"time":210696,"text":"from one hotel to another,"},{"time":213017,"text":"taking pictures from the windows\nof their buses of people and cultures,"},{"time":216988,"text":"but actually connecting with people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220169,"text":"You know, I remember having\na Muslim group from the U.K."},{"time":224093,"text":"going to the house\nof an Orthodox Jewish family,"},{"time":226879,"text":"and having their first Friday night\ndinners, that Sabbath dinner,"},{"time":231268,"text":"and eating together hamin,\nwhich is a Jewish food, a stew,"},{"time":234843,"text":"just having the connection\nof realizing, after a while,"},{"time":237722,"text":"that a hundred years ago,\ntheir families came out"},{"time":240694,"text":"of the same place in Northern Africa."},{"time":243773,"text":"This is not a photo profile\nfor your Facebook."},{"time":246848,"text":"This is not disaster tourism."},{"time":248682,"text":"This is the future of travel,"},{"time":251050,"text":"and I invite you to join me to do that,\nto change your travel."},{"time":254114,"text":"We're doing it all over the world now,"},{"time":256065,"text":"from Ireland to Iran to Turkey,"},{"time":258503,"text":"and we see ourselves going\neverywhere to change the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":261499,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":262729,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}